George Montgomery (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Montgomery_(actor) 0 George Montgomery (born George Montgomery Letz, August 29, 1916 – December 12, 2000) was an American actor, painter, sculptor, furniture craftsman, and stuntman who is best remembered as an actor in Western film and television.
